dataItem.name: probability of failure
dataItem.expression: CASE WHEN [percentile] between .9 and 1 THEN 5 WHEN [percentile] between .6 and .899999 THEN 4 WHEN [percentile] between .4 and .599999 THEN 3 WHEN [percentile] between .2 and .399999 THEN 2 ELSE 1 END

sqlQuery.name: SQL3
sqlQuery.sqlText:
select per_code, per_desc, sum(hrs) - sum(act_est) hrsover from ( select per_code, per_desc, hrs, act_est from r5events inner join r5objects on obj_code = evt_object inner join r5activities on act_event = evt_code inner join (select boo_event bevent, boo_act bact, boo_person, sum(boo_hours) hrs from r5bookedhours where boo_person is not null group by boo_event, boo_act, boo_person ) i on bevent = act_event and bact = act_act inner join r5personnel on per_code = boo_person where evt_rtype in ('PPM','JOB') and evt_jobtype != 'IS' and evt_status != 'REJ' and to_char(evt_target, 'YYYY-MM-DD') between #prompt('SEL_START')# and #prompt('SEL_END')# and ( #prompt('SEL_ORG')# = '%' or evt_org = #prompt('SEL_ORG')# ) and ( #prompt('SEL_MRC')# = '%' or evt_mrc = #prompt('SEL_MRC')# ) and ( #prompt('SEL_CLASS')# = '%' or obj_class = #prompt('SEL_CLASS')# ) and hrs > act_est and evt_jobtype <> 'MEC'
union select orl_supplier, 'Contractor: ' || orl_supplier, hrs, act_est from r5events inner join r5objects on obj_code = evt_object inner join r5activities on act_event = evt_code inner join (select boo_event bevent, boo_act bact, orl_supplier, sum(boo_hours) hrs from r5bookedhours inner join r5orderlines on orl_event = boo_event and orl_act = boo_act where boo_person is null and orl_type like 'S%' group by boo_event, boo_act, orl_supplier ) s on bevent = act_event and bact = act_act where evt_rtype in ('PPM','JOB') and evt_jobtype != 'IS' and evt_status != 'REJ' and to_char(evt_target, 'YYYY-MM-DD') between #prompt('SEL_START')# and #prompt('SEL_END')# and ( #prompt('SEL_ORG')# = '%' or evt_org = #prompt('SEL_ORG')# ) and ( #prompt('SEL_MRC')# = '%' or evt_mrc = #prompt('SEL_MRC')# ) and ( #prompt('SEL_CLASS')# = '%' or obj_class = #prompt('SEL_CLASS')# ) and hrs > act_est and evt_jobtype <> 'MEC' ) l
group by per_code, per_desc
